#

Tomato Basil Toast

15 min
$6.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Snack

Tags:

QuickHealthySnack

Description

A delightful blend of fresh tomatoes and fragrant basil atop crispy toast, perfect for a light meal or snack.

Ingredients

  • sourdough bread: 2 slices
  • fresh tomatoes: 1 cup, diced
  • fresh basil leaves: ¼ cup, chopped
  • mozzarella cheese: ½ cup, shredded
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: ¼ teaspoon
